    "body": "Before the fix, running `pytest tests/test_fp4_quantize.py` results in:\r\n```\r\nE           /workspace/flashinfer/csrc/nv_internal/tensorrt_llm/thop/fp4Op.cpp: In function ‘void mxfp4_dequantize_host(tvm::ffi::Tensor, tvm::ffi::Tensor, tvm::ffi::Tensor, int64_t)’:\r\nE           /workspace/flashinfer/csrc/nv_internal/tensorrt_llm/thop/fp4Op.cpp:309:35: error: base operand of ‘->’ has non-pointer type ‘tvm::ffi::ShapeView’                              \r\nE             309 |   TVM_FFI_ICHECK_NE(weight.shape()->Product(), 0) << \"weight should not be empty tensor\";                                                                              \r\nE                 |                                   ^~                                                                                                                                   \r\nE           /workspace/flashinfer/csrc/nv_internal/tensorrt_llm/thop/fp4Op.cpp:327:55: error: base operand of ‘->’ has non-pointer type ‘tvm::ffi::ShapeView’                             \r\nE             327 |   for (int packed_idx = 0; packed_idx < weight.shape()->Product(); ++packed_idx) {                                                                                     \r\nE                 |      \r\n```\r\n\r\nAfter the fix:\r\n```\r\n================================================================================= test session starts ===================================================================================platform linux -- Python 3.12.3, pytest-8.4.2, pluggy-1.6.0\r\nrootdir: /workspace/flashinfer\r\nconfigfile: pyproject.toml\r\ncollected 59 items\r\n\r\ntests/test_fp4_quantize.py ...........................................................                                                                                              [100%]\r\n\r\n=================================================================================== 59 passed in 4.76s ====================================================================================\r\n```",
